uwsinopia:general.uwsinopia:p: Use the Wikidata lookup to retrieve item IRIs for University of Washington shelving locations where available. Enter a location code as search string. For common location codes, see Location Codes for Ordering & Selecting Materials: Most Used*. (Page also includes a link to download a comprehensive list.)
Where no Wikidata item has been created for a needed shelving location, https://github.com/uwlib-cams/sinopia_maps/issues/new to request the needed Wikidata item.
